claim.claim-text:
A transformer comprising:
a bobbin having at least one first coupling unit formed at one end thereof;
a first assembling member having a second coupling unit formed to be selectively coupled to the first coupling unit;
a first pin member formed on the assembling member; and
a second pin member formed at the other end of the bobbin.
